# Qolsys Controller - qolsys-controller

[![Build](https://github.com/EHylands/QolsysController/actions/workflows/build.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/EHylands/QolsysController/actions/workflows/build.yml)

A Python module that emulates a virtual IQ Remote device, enabling full **local control** of a Qolsys IQ Panel over MQTT ‚Äî no cloud access required.

## QolsysController
- ‚úÖ Connects directly to the **Qolsys Panel's local MQTT server as an IQ Remote**
- üîê Pairs by only using **Installer Code** (same procedure as standard IQ Remote pairing)
- üî¢ Supports **4-digit user codes**
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Uses a **custom local usercode database** ‚Äî panel's internal user code verification process is not yet supported

